stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (WHY GOALS FEEL IMPOSSIBLE WITH ADHD) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (It's not willpower. It's executive function + dopamine.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (ADHD goal-setting challenges:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 652.2 Td (- We set too many goals \(shiny new goal syndrome\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (- We skip from 'idea' to 'done' without planning the middle) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (- We lose interest once novelty wears off) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.2 Td (- We feel shame about 'failed' goals and stop trying) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 586.4 Td (THIS workbook fixes these with:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 572.4 Td (- Only 3 goals at a time \(max!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 558.4 Td (- 90-day sprints \(not annual goals\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.4 Td (- Built-in 'is this still interesting?' checks) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.4 Td (- Permission to pivot \(goal funeral included\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.4 Td (- Micro-steps focus \(what's the TINIEST first action?\)) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
